HOUSE BILL 2603
By Salinas
SENATE BILL 2489
By Yarbro
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 4;
Title 7; Title 8; Title 12; Title 14; Title 33; Title 47;
Title 52; Title 53; Title 56; Title 62; Title 63; Title 68
and Title 71, relative to medicaid.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 71-5-105(a)(5), is amended by
deleting "sixty (60) days" and substituting "sixty-five (65) days".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
